

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Animated Hike Page</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: black;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Irish Grover', cursive;
    }

    .header {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: white;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: start;
    }

    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo-container img {
      height: 85px;
      width: auto;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-left: 680px;
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 150px; /* Adjust to avoid overlap with the fixed header */
    }

    .hike-text {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeIn 2s forwards, moveUp 2s forwards;
    }

    .lorem-text {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 20px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeIn 2s 3s forwards; /* 2s duration with 3s delay */
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes moveUp {
      to {
        transform: translateY(-20px);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <a href="/home">
        <img src="/images/Screenshot (58).png" alt="Logo">
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="hike-text">Hike</h1>
    <p class="lorem-text">Privacy Notice :<br>
      
This website respects your privacy. We are committed to protecting the privacy of our users and strive to provide a safe and secure online experience for all visitors. <br>

Information Collection and Use: <br>
- We do not collect any personally identifiable information unless you voluntarily provide it to us. <br>
- Any information you provide will only be used for the purpose for which you provided it. <br>
- We do not share your personal information with third parties without your consent, except as required by law. <br>
 <br>

 Security: <br>
- We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, misuse, or alteration. <br>
- However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security. <br>
      
  </div>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      const hikeText = document.querySelector('.hike-text');
      const loremText = document.querySelector('.lorem-text');

      setTimeout(() => {
        hikeText.classList.add('visible');
      }, 1000);

      setTimeout(() => {
        loremText.classList.add('visible');
      }, 1000);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
